<h1>mPDF</h1>
<h2>Tables</h2>
<h3>CSS Styles</h3>
<p>The CSS properties for tables and cells is increased over that in html2fpdf. It includes recognition of THEAD, TFOOT and TH.<br />See below for other facilities such as autosizing, and rotation.</p>
